{
  "texts": [
    "However, our VR NeRF framework is compatible with other VR headsets that support the SteamVR and OpenVR desktop runtime.",
    "To simulate how a user would perform virtual inspection tasks, we designed a visual search activity where the user was asked to locate three detailed components in the NeRF model based on a schematic sketch.",
    "As shown in Figures 7-(Instruction Card), the schematic sketch consisted of an overview of the CAD model, with each search target highlighted in a dialog box.",
    "Arrows are provided to indicate an approximate location where the detailed component might be found.",
    "The instructions for each search target were generated from the real-world images and therefore represent updated real-world conditions compared to the abstract CAD model."
  ]
}